title: Estonia  CPI Housing
description: CPI Housing Utilities in Estonia decreased to 585.75 points in October from 659.76 points in September of 2022. CPI Housing Utilities in Estonia averaged 228.25 points from 1994 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 683.04 points in August of 2022 and a record low of 32.80 points in January of 1994. This page provides - Estonia  Cpi Housing Utilities- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Statistics Estonia
